rows.label: tev001891_MSG0001
rows.name: Chief! What are you doing here?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001891_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev001891_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Mia who the man is beside her.

rows.label: tev001891_JNK0020
rows.name: Invite

rows.label: tev001891_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Mia to join you for dinner.

rows.label: tev001891_MSG0002
rows.name: Isn't it obvious? He's a client![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001891_MSG0003
rows.name:
Ooo, sorry. Right now I'm having an important
discussion with this client about a mission.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001891_MSG0004
rows.name: So while I'm thrilled to be invited, I have to decline.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001891_MSG0005
rows.name:
Anyway, could you maybe sorta...leave us alone now?
You're interrupting our delicate negotiations.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001891_JNK0030
rows.name: Worry

rows.label: tev001891_SEL0031
rows.name: Express concern about the nature of the client's mission.

rows.label: tev001891_JNK0040
rows.name: Lie

rows.label: tev001891_SEL0041
rows.name:
Say that you need Mia's help on a different
mission so she will quit pursuing this one.

rows.label: tev001891_JNK0050
rows.name: Assist

rows.label: tev001891_SEL0051
rows.name: Offer to work with Mia to complete the client's job.

rows.label: tev001891_MSG0006
rows.name:
Admittedly, this is an unusual place and time to meet
a client about a job, but I assure you there's nothing
suspicious about the request itself! Nope! Nuuuuh-uh.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001891_MSG0007
rows.name:
And I'll also remind you that I'm now a full-fledged
BLADE who can easily handle whatever type of mission
this cruel world sees fit to fling at her.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001891_MSG0008
rows.name:
Perhaps you're looking to get in on the job and divvy
up the reward money? I bet you are, you sly dog, you!
But the answer is still a big no.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001891_MSG0009
rows.name:
I'm gonna make like a bass and handle this job solo!
...Get it? Solo? "So low"? Bass? Never mind.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001891_MSG0010
rows.name: Anyway, please stop trying to get all up in my biz.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001891_MSG0011
rows.name: I appreciate your concern, Chief. I really do.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001891_MSG0012
rows.name: But my answer is still a big negatory.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001891_MSG0013
rows.name:
Plus, I know you don't have a mission for me.
You just made that up, you sly dog, you![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001891_MSG0014
rows.name:
And I'm too busy with my REAL mission to run around
chasing down your fake one.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001891_MSG0015
rows.name:
And I'll also remind you that I'm now a full-fledged
BLADE who can easily handle whatever type of mission
this cruel world sees fit to fling at her.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001891_MSG0016
rows.name: So please step up off my grill. Okay, Chief?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001891_MSG0017
rows.name: Nope! Tooootally not necessary.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001891_MSG0018
rows.name:
Hey, are you just looking to get in on the job and
divvy up the reward? I bet you are, you sly dog, you!
But the answer is still a big no.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001891_MSG0019
rows.name:
I'm gonna make like a bass and handle this job solo!
...Get it? Solo? "So low"? Bass? Never mind.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001891_MSG0020
rows.name:
Admittedly, this is an unusual place and time to meet
a client about a job, but I assure you there's nothing
suspicious about the request itself! Nope! Nuuuuh-uh.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001891_MSG0021
rows.name:
Juuust a normal job. Nothing special about it.
Almost boring, actually. Sleepy-time and all that.
Heck, the reward isn't even that good.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001891_MSG0022
rows.name:
And I'll also remind you that I'm now a full-fledged
BLADE who can easily handle whatever type of mission
this cruel world sees fit to fling at her.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001891_MSG0023
rows.name:
So make like a donut and roll on outta here!
...Er, donuts roll, right? The cake kind, at least?[ST:wait ]
